Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.42,0:00:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.09,0:00:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
