Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.21,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们大家救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.21,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me, everyone!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.88,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脾脏都露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.88,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your spleen is showing.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.84,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得感觉有一阵凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I felt a breeze!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来解决一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of that.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.43,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.43,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.18,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我照片恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.18,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My photo's back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.43,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  可是再看看这张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.43,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but take a look at this one!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.52,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从肥油里拔出海神黄金锅铲那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.52,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The time I pulled Neptune's spatula from the grease!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可拿着锅铲的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not holding it.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mom is!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mom is what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.73,0:01:32.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,去调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:32.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请看那终极厨具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold the ultimate cooking utensil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the golden spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写着  众多人试图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says here, "Many have tried
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从这远古肥油中拔出这把锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:46.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to pull this spatula from this ancient grease
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all have failed"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有配得上海神王本人的煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Only a fry cook worthy of King Neptune himself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can wield"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄金锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"the golden spatula"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我跟黄金锅铲合个影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a picture of me and the spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  给我干哪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness, where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.10,0:02:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别碰那脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, don't touch that filthy thing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不知道它都到过什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't know where it's been
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先给它擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just scrub it nice and clean
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  星妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mrs. Star
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亮晶晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So shiny
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能有人配得上皇家厨师的称号了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone worthy of being the royal fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁从肥油里拔出了我神奇的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who has freed my mighty spatula from the grease?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拔出锅铲的不可能是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way you pulled the spatula out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只是个卑贱的海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are but a lowly sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,puny
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无足轻重的弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an insignificant weakling
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这双无力的婴儿小手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, these feeble little baby arms
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝无可能释放出我神圣的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could never release my divine spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱离布满油污的监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from its greasy prison
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, your highness
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实拔出来的是我  星妈邦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was me, Bunny Star
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她朋友管她叫妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her friends call her "Mom"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你显然更胜一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are obviously superior
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你布满肌肉的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, look at your muscular arms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,592)}妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我天天打扫卫生  所以才这么壮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keeping things clean keeps me fit
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有着擎天神阿特拉斯的体格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have the physique of Atlas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我摆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make poses with me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的力量如此强大  有资格担任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clearly you possess the strength to become
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王的御厨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the personal chef of King Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没给神灵下过厨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never cooked for a deity before
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  邦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, Bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启程前往我的皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us depart to my palace
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在亚特兰蒂斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  星妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Mrs. Star
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏板得你来蹬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll need to pedal
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请看我神圣的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold my divine kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神的厨房最适合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a kitchen of the gods
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来整点简单的家常菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to whip up a simple home-cooked meal
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽情品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a taste
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么不同寻常的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that unusual flavor?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这上等美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's just the delicious flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的招牌靴子面汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of my famous boot noodle soup
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just lost my appetite
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这大神还在长身体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a big growing god
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.14,0:04:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  有人拉肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my, someone has a case of the rumblies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in their tummy wummy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带你上床  把你给养好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get you in bed, mister, and fix you up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寡人的日程今天排得满满当当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My kingly docket is incredibly full today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我病得不轻  恐怕无法尽职了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm far too ill to complete my royal duties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever shall I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  我来帮你尽职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, I'll handle all your royal business
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么知道尽什么职呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how will I know what to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当我的王国危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When my kingdom is in peril
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我强大的三叉戟都会大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my mighty trident will glow
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指引你前去济世救民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and take you to where you are needed
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  但你到底多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but when was the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没好好把这三叉戟擦干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you gave this trident a good scrubbing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.60,0:05:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那把三叉戟可是亚特兰蒂斯远古文物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That trident is an ancient Atlantean artifact
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万万不能用擦洗剂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No abrasive cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得上工了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.78,0:05:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要好好休息哦  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be sure you get lots of rest, sweetie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,372)}裤头村小学
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这些小鱼儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the little guppies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛要带我来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, why did you take me here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  可不能让那个掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness, we can't have that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算重新粉刷完了海之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally finished repainting the Chum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,754)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, kiddies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个洞也不能破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't have that either
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么收拾干净呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I gonna clean all this up?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was easy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:52.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1404,852)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被禁足了  大洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are grounded, Mr. Flood
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回你房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to your room
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,700,0,,感谢那个谁  都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,700,0,,Thank someone that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.40,0:07:46.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  有谁发了点小脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:46.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, someone's having a little temper tantrum
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你冷静一点  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you just settle down, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是有人在乎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anyone cares
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赞美邦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Praise Bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赞美邦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Praise Bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knew?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要稍微假装一下肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I needed to do was fake a bellyache
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.47,0:08:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能放上千载难逢的第一个假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'd have my first day off in a millennia
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要中断本节目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt this program
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,238)}海胆哥与败蜗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,564)}突发新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播裤头村突发新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Bikini Bottom breaking news
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帕奇帕金斯正在现场报道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch Perkins here reporting live
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村新晋的大英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on Bikini Bottom's newest hero
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星妈邦妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bunny Star
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问一下  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如何评价我们新晋的守护天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think of our new guardian angel?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了邦妮女王  就用不上海神王了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs King Neptune when we have Queen Bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邦妮女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Queen Bunny?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是有谁敢比我红  我绝对不能忍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for anyone being more popular than me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以这位就是你们新晋的女王了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, this is your new Queen, is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星妈邦妮  我要向你发起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bunny Star, I challenge thee
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极挑战擂台赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the ultimate contest
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当场完成艰巨任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A herculean task
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.31,0:09:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从此决出谁才是海底真神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to divine who is the true god of the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就很乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a hoot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard it here first, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真神擂台赛开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for a god-off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,344)}海神波塞殿
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到海神波塞殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Poseidome
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两位神灵将在此角逐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where two powerful deities will battle it out
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,争夺海神的王位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Neptune's crown
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,究竟哪位泰坦大神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which one of these mighty titans
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能击败凶残的克拉肯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can defeat the savage Kraken?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.10,0:09:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我海神王  将会击败克拉肯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, King Neptune, will defeat the Kraken
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用到的武器正是我的旧三叉戟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll do it using my old trident
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二叉戟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bident
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.82,0:10:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放出克拉肯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Release the Kraken
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快带你妈走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, Patrick, grab your mom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你的新造型  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love your new look, Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not your mom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只剩我们两个了  克拉肯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's just you and me, Kraken
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝我海神王的怒火  你这肮脏野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taste the mighty fury of Neptune, you foul beast
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你管谁叫肮脏野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who you callin' foul beast?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自己也没好看到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're no beauty queen yourself, fella
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下想起来干嘛要雪藏这旧东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I remember why I put this old thing in storage
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你三叉戟还在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still have your trident
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我还特地给它擦干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I made sure to give it a good scrubbing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受我无敌三叉戟的神力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel the might of my invincible trident
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早跟她说过不能用擦洗剂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told her no abrasive cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道原来海神王这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knew Neptune tasted so good?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改天还要再吃他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll try him a second time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是旷工的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what I get for playing hooky from work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这味道就是鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tastes like chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,à la King
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.73,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,救回老妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.73,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We rescued Mom!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好检查一下照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'd better check the photo.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  都恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune, it's back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不太应该感谢海神王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not sure we should be thanking Neptune for anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷还在迷离时空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat is still lost in time!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.58,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查一下别的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.58,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's check the other photos!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在蟹堡王上班的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My first day working at the Krusty Krab!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.46,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.46,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not me.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's GrandPat!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道派大爷会下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know GrandPat could cook!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.93,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看是怎么个事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.93,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's see what happened.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特好看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:32.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be good!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.36,0:12:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.74,0:12:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有史以来最棒的提供饮食的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The finest eating establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever established for eating
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:59.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(546,448)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡之家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Home of the Krabby Patty"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,窗户上还贴着招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a "Help Wanted" sign in the--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1046,342)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了  派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是我们新任的煎炸厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're our new fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你给旧日损友干活不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not a problem working for your old frenemy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没给你干活呢  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not working for you, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是在你旁边干活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm working near you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说了算  老东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, old-timer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:49.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,376)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个送报纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the paperboy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就没在给你送报纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your paperboy anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我心中  你永远都在给我送报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To me you'll always be my paperboy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送报纸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paperboy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.64,0:13:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在全世界最好的水下餐厅都下过厨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've worked in the world's finest underwater kitchens
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比方说从凡尔赛的喷泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From the fountains of Versailles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再到泰姬陵的倒影池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the reflecting pool of the Taj Mahal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这垃圾堆轻轻松松就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can easily handle this dump
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给自己来整点东西吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll make myself something to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.08,0:14:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来像舱门打开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounded like hatch doors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你闻到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you smell it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That smell
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某种难闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A kind of smelly smell
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这难闻的味道  味道又很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A smelly smell that smells
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只闻到了凤尾鱼味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I smell are anchovies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchovies?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchovies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做蟹黄堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start cooking Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pronto
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要求你们排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One single file line is all I ask
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The heck with this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁呲我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's psssssting me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看下面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  我付你一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tell ya what, I'll give you one dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买那个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for that Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这蟹黄堡太大了  你这小不点吃不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This patty's too big for a little squirt like you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这就叫胃口大  肚子小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your eye is bigger than your stomach
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没要拿来吃  你个白痴无脊椎动物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna eat it, you imbecilic invertebrate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿它有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need it for, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别的用途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,something else
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话  就给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case you can have it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,条件是先给我付五百块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for five hundred smackers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是比杀手机器人便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still cheaper than a killer robot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不吃是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not gonna eat it, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.82,0:16:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是打算把那蟹黄堡怎么了  矮冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha plannin' on doin'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with that Krabby Patty, short stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你真要问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you must know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rule the world
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先我会复制这个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I'll replicate this patty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:34.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,156)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着用卖蟹黄堡赚来的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then with all the money I make from selling them
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,召集一支可怕的克隆大军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll raise a terrifying clone army
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,占领全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to take over the whole world
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之后呢  谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After that, who knows?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多半还要单纯找个乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe, just for the heck of it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火烧全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll burn it all down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后那句你别传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That last part is just between us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要什么时候开始找这个乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When's all this fun gonna start?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我按下那颗红色按钮就能开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As soon as I push that red button
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那颗按钮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That button?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着挺复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks complicated
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯就一颗小按钮罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple little button
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便哪个白痴都可以按
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any idiot can push it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便哪个白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any idiot?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便哪个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This button?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便哪个白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any idiot?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I said
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便哪个白痴都可以按
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any idiot can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.14,0:17:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一件事你没有考虑到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one thing you hadn't planned on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是随便哪个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm any idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方已取得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formula acquired
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大爷堡万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hail the Grand Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,730)}海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,730)}大爷堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,218)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,542)}大爷堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1104,676)}蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1522,750)}大爷堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1548,558)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1548,558)}大爷堡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222,670)}大爷复制缸
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本大王接下来的毁灭行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For my next royal act of destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.99,0:18:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要把全天下烧个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will set all of creation on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再烧一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马屁精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suck-ups
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按理来说那是我的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By all rights, that idea was mine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被拍马屁的应该是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should be sucking up to me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对于计划挺有品味的  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had good taste in plans, tiny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来吃吃看你是不是真有味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's see if you have actual good taste
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.90,0:18:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pain
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样啊  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you like that, Krabsy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前亲自打爆他才比较爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I liked it better when I used to smush him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时旅柜完完全全发癫错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Time Closet went all wack-a-doodle ding-dong
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不该来这里的  派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here, GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们要带你回到正确的时间线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we've come to return you to your proper timeline
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Intruders
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guards
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.76,0:19:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,押走他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take them away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就不能最后吃一餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't we get one last meal?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那办法对我们行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't work out for us.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.31,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道对世界行不行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the rest of the world did.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.61,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是别那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.61,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's not do that.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这次先砸晕他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time let's clobber him first!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个更好的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a better solution.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要倒退一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just rewind a bit and...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.91,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家进时旅柜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.91,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody, into the Time Closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:55.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,174)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一把水动力锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hydro-dynamic spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带左右铲的配件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with port and starboard attachments
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有涡轮发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and turbo drive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  零钱不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, keep the change
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带着这把锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take this spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞去蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fly to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save the day
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trust me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁  美丽的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you, beautiful stranger?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有点眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look kinda familiar
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是一个小海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just a simple sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有着一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a job
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你也有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you have one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  谁准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, who's ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, GrandPat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起回到现代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the present
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还要炒股
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was gonna play the stock market
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投资高菲高伯才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and invest in Goofy Goober's
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道是谁赢了泡泡碗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who wins the Bubble Bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  达奇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dutch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我多厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at me go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that all about?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落地不超过五秒就还能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five-second rule
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.16,0:21:52.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:52.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说派大爷末日成功阻止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you think we averted the GrandPat apocalypse?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小鬼头给刚刚的事件取了这个名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what the kids are calling it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.29,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个办法能找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.29,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看着挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty normal to me!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:11.60,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1348,905)}老奶奶村
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grannyville?!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了带回章鱼老奶奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We forgot about Granny Tentacles!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.81,0:22:19.73,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶女皇驾到  闲杂人等退散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:19.73,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for Empress Granny!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.44,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这张一定得贴进我剪贴簿里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.44,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one's for sure going in my scrapbook!
